reviewText: Effective but 2 of the 10 min workouts I have on other Golds Gym DVDs
For a short video, i def felt it! Great way to start getting active again after baby! Its was nice being anle to choose different workouts too. Also quick videos for moms on the go.

Equipment recommended with this DVD: resistance tube or band, exercise mat and stability ball. With this high quality DVD, you can: (1) tighten and tone (2) build muscle (3) enhance flexibility (4) strengthen core (5) lose weight, and (6) increase cardio

As with any exercise program, consult your physician before you begin!
